---
import { SITE, NAV, WHATSAPP_LINK, INSTAGRAM, CATALOG_PDF } from "@/lib/site";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative border-t border-line bg-ink">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 md:px-10 md:py-24">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:grid-cols-[1.5fr_1fr_1fr]">
      <div>
        <img src="/ebm-logo.png" alt={SITE.name} class="mb-5 h-12 w-auto" />
        <p class="editorial max-w-sm text-lg text-muted">
          “Cada libra importa. Precisão técnica para o seu jogo.”
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 font-body text-sm text-faint">
          Encordoamento de raquetes de tênis em <span class="text-papel"
            >Florianópolis</span
          > e São José · busca e entrega.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="tech-label mb-4 text-faint">Navegar</h4>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          {
            NAV.map((item) => (
              <li>
                <a
                  href={item.href}
                  class="font-display text-xl uppercase text-papel transition-colors hover:text-lima"
                >
                  {item.label}
                </a>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="tech-label mb-4 text-faint">Contato</h4>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <li>
            <a
              href={WHATSAPP_LINK}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="font-display text-xl uppercase text-papel transition-colors hover:text-lima"
              >WhatsApp</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href={INSTAGRAM}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="font-display text-xl uppercase text-papel transition-colors hover:text-lima"
              >Instagram</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href={CATALOG_PDF}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              download
              class="font-display text-xl uppercase text-papel transition-colors hover:text-lima"
              >Catálogo PDF ↓</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-4 border-t border-line pt-8 md:flex-row md:items-center"
    >
      <span class="font-mono text-xs text-faint"
        >© {year} {SITE.name} · {SITE.domain}</span
      >
      <span class="tech-label text-faint">Performance começa nas cordas</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
